# ─── Big binary assets that exceed GitHub's 100MB limit ──
# Both copies (source `models/` and runtime `app/public/models/`).
# These live in Google Drive — see DRIVE_ASSETS.md for download +
# placement instructions when cloning on a fresh machine.

# Kratos — Blade of Chaos (~222MB)
models/blade_of_chaos_-_god_of_war.glb
app/public/models/kratos.glb

# Druid — Werewolf (~122MB)
models/armoured_werewolf_warlord_-_untextured_meshy_6.glb
app/public/models/druid.glb

# (Other heavies stay in repo: guts 64MB, skybox 52MB, aatrox 15MB,
#  knot 4.5MB, ichigo 5.8MB, anatomy 14MB. GitHub warns >50MB but
#  accepts them. If you want a leaner repo, also ignore guts/skybox.)
